## Pricing copy: always "up to X", never "X"

```html
<!-- ✅ correct -->
<li>Up to <strong class="text-ink">40</strong> findings + fix prompts</li>

<!-- ❌ wrong — implies a guarantee -->
<li><strong class="text-ink">40</strong> findings + fix prompts</li>
```

